{"arkId":"cl010099914","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010099914","modified ":"2025-11-18","title":"Montre en forme de t\u00eate de mort","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre en forme de t\u00eate de mort"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XIV (1643-1715) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1640 - 1660","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 2","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1640,"endYear":1660,"imprecision":"","text":"Milieu du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Rousseau, Jean","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1606","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1684","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 8314","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Bo\u00eete cr\u00e2nienne formant la cuvette du bo\u00eetier et la macho\u00eere inf\u00e9rieure, articul\u00e9e par une charni\u00e8re, sert de couvercle au cadran. Cr\u00e2ne reperc\u00e9 et grav\u00e9 de rinceaux fleuris. Deux m\u00e9daillons, r\u00e9serv\u00e9s, sont grav\u00e9s : Adam et Eve, sur le front et, La R\u00e9surrection, derri\u00e8re le cr\u00e2ne ; banderole grav\u00e9e de sentences entourant ce d\u00e9cor : Stipendia Peccati mors. Domun (Saint Paul, Rom., 6\/23) \/ Sicut in Adamo omnes moriuntur \/ ita \u0026 in Christo omnes uiuificabutur (Saint Paul, 1 Cor., 15\/22). Anneau de suspension au-dessus du cr\u00e2ne. Cadran \u00e0 chiffres romains. A l\u0027int\u00e9rieur, cercle mobile grav\u00e9 de chiffres arabes marquant l\u0027heure du r\u00e9veil, d\u00e9cor\u00e9 au centre de rinceaux fleuris ; index fix\u00e9 sur le 12 rempla\u00e7ant l\u0027aiguille des heures habituelle. Mouvement \u00e0 r\u00e9veil dot\u00e9 d\u0027un \u00e9chappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre, une fus\u00e9e avec cha\u00eenette. Barillet de la sonnerie grav\u00e9 et reperc\u00e9 de rinceaux fleuris comme le coq \u00e0 un pied. Vis-sans-fin munie d\u0027une rosette de r\u00e9glage num\u00e9rot\u00e9e.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : Jean Rousseau","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"5,5","displayDimension":"5,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"4,5","displayDimension":"4,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton\r\nTechnique : dor\u00e9 = dorure (techniques m\u00e9tal)","placeOfCreation":"Gen\u00e8ve (Europe-\u003ESuisse)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"collection Jules-Ren\u00e9 Olivier (1855-1933), horloger-collectionneur ; legs de sa s\u0153ur Marie-Julie Olivier, n\u00b0 807 ; comit\u00e9 du 24 janvier 1935 ; conseil du 5 f\u00e9vrier 1935 ; d\u00e9cret du 4 ao\u00fbt 1935","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme Olivier, Marie-Julie","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"Olivier, Jules-Ren\u00e9","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"24\/01\/1935","startYear":1935,"endYear":1935},{"type":"date du conseil","value":"05\/02\/1935","startYear":